Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Những hành động của anh không phải tất cả đều chính xác
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hãy trả lời câu hỏi của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.70,0:00:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baek San và Sa Woo giết hại giọng nói đó,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}và giọng nói đó đã chuyển cho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyun Jun quá trình mình bị hại
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,làm cho người khác đổ máu,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,nhất định sẽ trả giá bằng máu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tập 14
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Đừng nghĩ rằng mọi chuyện sẽ kết thúc như thế này
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bởi vì có thể kết thúc sự việc này
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Trước giờ đều không phải là tôi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ông vẫn có thể nói vậy, sau từng ấy năm ư
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,chuyện này
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.78,0:01:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cho dù là quốc gia
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,hoặc là người giống như tiến sĩ đây
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bất kỳ một tổ chức nào chống lại IRIS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Đều không thể may mắn mà thoát nạn được
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nếu như ông nghĩ rằng Hyun Jun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,có thể cho ông hi vọng
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,chúng tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Để cho nó sống chẳng qua chỉ vì nó còn có ích
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,chỉ cần tôi muốn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thì bất cứ lúc nào tôi cũng có thể giết chết nó
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ông còn điều gì cần nói không?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Làm người khác đổ máu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhất định phải trả bằng máu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Đó…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Câu 6, chương 9 kinh cựu ước
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi sẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghi nhớ nó
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,không... không được
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi sẽ xem xung quanh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,có thể bọn họ đã đi rồi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,không còn ai cả
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ông còn điều gì cần nói không?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Làm người khác đổ máu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nhất định sẽ phải trả giá bằng máu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Đó...
